response.original_title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 10
response.overview: Day 10 of NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017 took place on October 30, 2017 at Korakuen Hall in Tokyo, Japan and was broadcast on Samurai! TV.  The main event featured Roppongi 3K (SHO & YOH) vs Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI & Hiromu Takahashi).  The card also featured ACH & Ryusuke Taguchi vs Suzuki-gun (El Desperado & Yoshinobu Kanemaru).  Other wrestlers on the show include Jushin Thunder Liger, Tiger Mask, and Hiroshi Tanahashi and more!
response.title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 10
